languages.text: "Да вот думаю, что за возвышенное и трогательное чувство — первая влюбленность! Эти бабочки в животе, этот жар на щеках..."
"I was just wondering what this soaring, stirring feeling was — first love! Ah, I can feel the butterflies in my belly, the heat in my cheeks..."

languages.text: “我只是在想，你这种酸酸涩涩、惴惴不安的心情应该就是——初恋！啊，我感到蝴蝶在胸中振翅，红晕爬上脸颊……”
languages.original_text: "I was just wondering what this soaring, stirring feeling was — first love! Ah, I can feel the butterflies in my belly, the heat in my cheeks..."

traits.locale_text: “我只是在想，你这种酸酸涩涩、惴惴不安的心情应该就是——初恋！啊，我感到蝴蝶在胸中振翅，红晕爬上脸颊……”

languages.text: « Je me demandais juste ce qu'était ce sentiment montant en moi... le premier amour ! Ah, j'ai l'impression d'avoir les joues en feu, sans parler des papillons dans le ventre... »
languages.original_text: "I was just wondering what this soaring, stirring feeling was — first love! Ah, I can feel the butterflies in my belly, the heat in my cheeks..."

languages.text: «Me estaba preguntando qué era esta sensación tan ardiente y estimulante... ¡el primer amor! Ah, siento las mariposas en la tripa, el calor en las mejillas...».
languages.original_text: "I was just wondering what this soaring, stirring feeling was — first love! Ah, I can feel the butterflies in my belly, the heat in my cheeks..."

traits.locale_text: «Me estaba preguntando qué era esta sensación tan ardiente y estimulante... ¡el primer amor! Ah, siento las mariposas en la tripa, el calor en las mejillas...».

languages.text: 「この高鳴るような、かき立てられるような感覚は…初恋じゃないかなって思ってたところよ！ああ、お腹がぞわぞわして、頬が熱くなるのを感じる…」
languages.original_text: "I was just wondering what this soaring, stirring feeling was — first love! Ah, I can feel the butterflies in my belly, the heat in my cheeks..."

traits.locale_text: 「この高鳴るような、かき立てられるような感覚は…初恋じゃないかなって思ってたところよ！ああ、お腹がぞわぞわして、頬が熱くなるのを感じる…」

languages.text: "Ich habe mich nur gefragt, was dieses schwebende, belebende Gefühl war ... die erste Liebe! Ach, ich spüre die Schmetterlinge im Bauch, die Hitze in meinen Wangen ..."
languages.original_text: "I was just wondering what this soaring, stirring feeling was — first love! Ah, I can feel the butterflies in my belly, the heat in my cheeks..."

languages.text: "Bu muazzam, karmaşık duyuların adını koyamıyordum da... İlk aşkmış! Ah, yanaklarım kıpkırmızı, karnımda kelebekler..."
